# PART 2
light are configured by level of brightness.
	turn on increases the birghtness by 1
	turn off decreases the brightness by 1
	toggle increases the brightness by 2

WHAT IS THE TOTAL BRIGHTNESS OF ALL LIGHTS COMBINED?
